<div class="px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="sm:flex sm:items-center">
      <div class="sm:flex-auto">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-6 text-gray-900">Catálogo de Prestadores</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-700">Lista completa gerenciável. Toda alteração ficará pendente de compilação na fila abaixo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-4 sm:ml-16 sm:mt-0 sm:flex-none">
        <a href="/admin/partner/new" class="block rounded-md bg-gray-800 px-3 py-2 text-center text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-700">Adicionar Parceiro</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Alert Panel para o Rebuild -->
    <% if (dirtyCount > 0) { %>
    <div class="mt-6 rounded-md bg-yellow-50 p-4 border border-yellow-200">
        <div class="flex">
            <div class="ml-3">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-yellow-800">Atenção Necessária: <%= dirtyCount %> cidade(s) com dados pendentes.</h3>
            <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-yellow-700">
                <p>Alterações recentes foram salvas com sucesso no banco de dados, mas o site público ainda apresenta a versão antiga. Dispare o motor no cabeçalho ou agurde a Cron para refletir as novidades no ar.</p>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="mt-8 flow-root">
      <div class="-mx-4 -my-2 overflow-x-auto sm:-mx-6 lg:-mx-8">
        <div class="inline-block min-w-full py-2 align-middle sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
          <div class="overflow-hidden shadow ring-1 ring-black ring-opacity-5 sm:rounded-lg">
            <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-gray-300">
              <thead class="bg-gray-50">
                <tr>
                  <th scope="col" class="py-3.5 pl-4 pr-3 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 sm:pl-6">Empresa</th>
                  <th scope="col" class="px-3 py-3.5 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Plano</th>
                  <th scope="col" class="px-3 py-3.5 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Vencimento</th>
                  <th scope="col" class="px-3 py-3.5 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900">Status</th>
                  <th scope="col" class="relative py-3.5 pl-3 pr-4 sm:pr-6">
                    <span class="sr-only">Ações</span>
                  </th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-gray-200 bg-white">
                <% if (listings.length === 0) { %>
                    <tr><td colspan="5" class="p-6 text-center text-sm text-gray-500">Nenhum prestador cadastrado localmente. Puxe a base do IBGE ou comece a adicionar parceiros.</td></tr>
                <% } else { %>
                    <% listings.forEach(function(l) { %>
                    <tr>
                    <td class="whitespace-nowrap py-4 pl-4 pr-3 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 sm:pl-6"><%= l.company_name %></td>
                    <td class="whitespace-nowrap px-3 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500 uppercase"><%= l.plan_level %></td>
                    <td class="whitespace-nowrap px-3 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500"><%= l.last_renewal_date ? new Date(l.last_renewal_date).toLocaleDateString() : 'N/A' %></td>
                    <td class="whitespace-nowrap px-3 py-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
                        <% if (l.is_active) { %>
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-green-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-green-700 border border-green-200">Ativo</span>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-md bg-red-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-red-700 border border-red-200">Inativo/Rebaixado</span>
                        <% } %>
                    </td>
                    <td class="relative whitespace-nowrap py-4 pl-3 pr-4 text-right text-sm font-medium sm:pr-6">
                        <a href="/admin/partner/<%= l.id %>" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-900">Editar</a>
                    </td>
                    </tr>
                    <% }); %>
                <% } %>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
</div>
